comments: VanVleet (TOR) is moving alongside Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Dinwiddie's drive.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of defensive goaltending was confirmed. 
 Hernangomez (TOR) makes contact with the rim that causes the backboard to shake, which affects Dinwiddie's (DAL) shot attempt.
Young (TOR) is already in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and is firming up when he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Kleber (DAL) is retreating alongside Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the marginal contact as he defends the shot near the rim.
Bullock (DAL) is already in Anunoby's (TOR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
All Flagrant Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Boucher (TOR) legally contests Bullock's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Hernangomez (TOR) during rebounding.
Anunoby (TOR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Dinwidde (DAL) as they pursue the rebound.
Dinwiddie's (DAL) left hand makes contact with the ball, and any ensuing contact with Anunoby's (TOR) head is considered marginal.  A jump ball is correctly called.
Boucher (TOR) briefly grasps Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm, and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Raptors.
Young (TOR) is already in FInney-Smith's (DAL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Anunoby (TOR) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) moves alongside Anunoby's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Hernangomez (TOR) moves alongside Dinwiddie's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Young (TOR) brings his arm towards Kleber (DAL), and marginal contact occurs as he receives the pass.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Anunoby (TOR) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Kleber (DAL) is moving alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) is already in VanVleet's (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Dinwiddie (DAL) and VanVleet (TOR) briefly engage and disengage off ball.

Bullock (DAL) moves forward into Boucher's (TOR) lower body and initiates contact as he contests the shot attempt.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred prior to the expiration of the shot clock.
Anunoby (TOR) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) moves somewhat laterally towards Anunoby (TOR), and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Green (DAL) briefly grasps Young's (TOR) jersey during the inbound, and the contact is marginal.
Green (DAL) commits a take foul on Young (TOR).
Kleber (DAL) is already in VanVleet's (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Anunoby (TOR).
